{"tid":1579652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到底9月22有咩活動？","createTime":"2019-09-18T16:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T16:29:00.000Z","uid":12405,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"71c80025b7086c3bb03c83548cee6fbe33747da6","tid":1579652,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"如題 和理塞 定係去領事館 定係塞商場？"},{"pid":"6672e68f2413d25ea0fd54829e213f3fcc48f7d1","tid":1579652,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:17:54.000Z","msg":"【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！快閃式萬國「民主」旗號召世界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eccnjS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eccnjS</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n由於香港身為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>東道主</strong></span></span>倘若因為任何原因而令到遊行人數小得難睇, 是不理想的！<br />\n<br />\n同埋我寧願<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>10.1國殤</strong></span>打到拆天就最好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當然大家請記著呢日唔是End-game<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 由美帝反共眾議員可以見到場戰爭並非一朝一夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 失去所有勇武運動將難以持續<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家講到星期日9.29是全球性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 單靠香港人文宣團隊twitter retweet比當地人是難以收到巨大宣傳效益<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">唯有無比juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />方法去呼喚他國人民, 同埋件事夠juicy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />外國媒體先會幫你免費頭版</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong>【9.23~9.27】全球「反共」聯軍來了我帶路！<br />\n集合時間：1930~2000<br />\n遊行時間：2000~終點和平散去 (預計9點前行到遮打即龍頭散去)<br />\n舉行日期：9月23日至9月27日晚上快閃式遊行<br />\n遊行路線：修頓球場 至 遮打花園<br />\n注意事項：遊行完就即時由中環遮打盡快散去！不起衝突！人小就行行人路<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n衣著：遊行時黑色, 前往及離開時非黑色<br />\n快閃遊行目的：號召全球「反共」聯軍同時響應9.29大遊行, 盡可能與香港同步舉行！</strong></span><br />\n利申：是次遊行屬自發性質, 沒有不反對通知書<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講到反共你走去申請唔好傻啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我主張每晚均可見到頭60名民主國度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只要有60位手足舉60支旗個畫面已經夠晒Juicy<br />\n首先你話該國家一直龜縮有咩撚用,舉嚟把撚啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是9.29反共大遊行號召目標是各國人民,<br />\n如果我地真是連續一星期舉民主國家國旗, <span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>當地右翼會相當自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>,<br />\n同埋每晚我地可以twitter開放檢討比各國人民知道其國旗在香港揚起以打倒中共</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b73d2c6a44f29d1382ffa788469e41afdd172f6","tid":1579652,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"[907機場] 詳細分析907狗畜當日佈防及策略，附未來破陣建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d53dcc02e19a6d106713447de5305d0ce8075f66","tid":1579652,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c80025b7086c3bb03c83548cee6fbe33747da6","tid":1579652,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"如題 和理塞 定係去領事館 定係塞商場？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:19:07.000Z","msg":"和理塞+塞商場<br />\n個人預計情況不樂觀, 有被捕risk+抄牌和理塞&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;塞商場, 驚人流shift左"},{"pid":"8f5afd33e2b11af79199428c72229386b2d51a62","tid":1579652,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9720293f66deecaf894b909973881b5a0d9206","tid":1579652,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f39865cf6ddded6414eaad55d22370e72ce8765","tid":1579652,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:23:01.000Z","msg":"搵埋律師入機場，直接同佢張禁制令開波啦"},{"pid":"f8b9d230953df6de9f81fb070befffaee6b150b0","tid":1579652,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4173d97d18c8a331bd09b1e5031c8f6b347d781c","tid":1579652,"uid":12405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eac961cee56db79391e37103854a0da498486c","tid":1579652,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b73d2c6a44f29d1382ffa788469e41afdd172f6","tid":1579652,"uid":124134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:18:58.000Z","msg":"[907機場] 詳細分析907狗畜當日佈防及策略，附未來破陣建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1579570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1579570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:27:45.000Z","msg":"有用post 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639e7911f5efee317d0ade1e4d2594db2179ca0c","tid":1579652,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"覺得自己應該去就去<br />\n驚少人冇效果就再判斷"}]}